Text: Ah that's hella frustrating. On the bright side, though, I guess at least they are concerned about your health. I hope you can get what you need soon!

Author: catsinsunglassess
Text: I’m hoping my doctor will give me something soon. I’m literally jumping through every fucking hoop to get medication and they are just making me wait and wait and wait and try other things.
